{"tid":2113564,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"離心出現？美斯怒批巴塞後社交平台開始關注曼城……","createTime":"2020-07-18T08:17:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T02:38:17.000Z","uid":173952,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"103b433bc5c7fea2df51fa351e68e27b76420e2e","tid":2113564,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T08:17:49.000Z","msg":"在輸掉西甲冠軍之爭後，美斯（Lionel Messi）批評巴塞「脆弱」、「不穩定」。而在那之後，有人稱他開始在社交平台上關注曼城。<br />\n<br />\n  曼城TV主持人Natalie Paweleck稱，在Instagram平台上，美斯新加上了對曼城的關注，這立刻引發了曼城球迷的猜測：<br />\n<br />\n  「美斯在Instagram上關注了曼城，這是否有什麼意味？」<br />\n<br />\n  「美斯關注曼城了，這是一個信號嗎？真的要發生了嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n  「美斯真想來曼城了？」<br />\n<br />\n曼城TV女主持的曝料<br />\n<br />\n  不過也有球迷駁斥了Natalie Paweleck的說法，他們指出，美斯關注曼城其實已經有一段時間了，還關注了曼城的阿根廷球星阿古路（Sergio Aguero）和奧達文迪（Nicolas Otamendi）。而且在Instagram上，美斯關注的英超球隊還有車路士。"},{"pid":"0defb33a1be00be6bbfba212fc615cbd0986b304","tid":2113564,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T08:18:52.000Z","msg":"N年前佢都科勞過曼城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34f4862f1d58cf0414ce6a38e9a9eed4981723db","tid":2113564,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0defb33a1be00be6bbfba212fc615cbd0986b304","tid":2113564,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T08:18:52.000Z","msg":"N年前佢都科勞過曼城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T08:19:56.000Z","msg":"25仔"},{"pid":"4412716b924f143f83c5f380cdec5597af532557","tid":2113564,"uid":45772,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T08:21:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i2-prod.mirror.co.uk/incoming/article9294123.ece/ALTERNATES/s615/messimockup2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2-prod.mirror.co.uk%2Fincoming%2Farticle9294123.ece%2FALTERNATES%2Fs615%2Fmessimockup2.jpg&h=0d657afb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"74ae38cc2dc13cd483a85ded846cdc0e428d44e4","tid